msContents.summary: Magical texts, including Šimmuš ha-Tehillim; a mishnaic glossary for the tractates Šabbat, Pesaḥim, Yoma, Sukka, and Beṣa.

msItem.title: Lexicography; Talmud; magical; halaḵa
msItem.textLang: Hebrew (sporadic Tiberian and Babylonian vocalisation); Aramaic; Judaeo-Arabic
msItem.note: The fragments preserve miscellaneous material written in different hands.
